    (H4( sid.1 ) @ #l.1)
   ⇒
    ((∃ bPrimeb. (ba.1 = sg(bPrimeb, sskDa.1))) ∨ (S.1 = S))) ∧
  (∀ a #i.1. (Corrupted( a ) @ #i.1) ⇒ a = S)"
*/
by sorry

